# Purchase Assistant — MASTER agent rules

**Session start:** Read `CURRENT_CONTEXT.md`, `PROGRESS_LOG.md`, and `docs/harisree/MASTER_REFERENCE.md` before coding (Harisree product truth: infra, UX, pages, deploy). Index: `docs/harisree/README.md`.

